  m_Text: 'You can transition to other scenes by using Unity''s built-in SceneManager.LoadScene("Your
    Scene Name");


    VRIF also includes a helper script called "SceneLoader" you
    may use to load a scene with a nice Fade effect, which uses VRIF''s  built-in
    "ScreenFader" component.


    TIp : Make sure you have your scenes added to
    your project''s Build Settings.'
