    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "FloodSafe VR is an immersive virtual reality experience designed to educate
    players on how to respond during a real flood emergency. It puts you in the shoes
    of a flood survivor \u2014 forcing you to make quick decisions, prioritize essential
    supplies, and find a safe escape route.\n\nBuilt to promote flood preparedness
    and awareness, FloodSafe VR turns critical survival knowledge into an unforgettable
    hands-on experience that stays with you long after you take off the headset."
