  m_Text: "A flood warning has been issued. The water is rising. Here is what you
    must do:\n\n\U0001F3E0 1. Gather Supplies \u2014 Collect essentials before the
    water gets in\n\n\U0001F6AA 2. Escape the House \u2014 Get out before it's too
    late\n\n\U0001FAB5 3. Find a Floating Object \u2014 Use debris to navigate the
    flooded streets\n\n\U0001F3E2 4. Reach the Tallest Building \u2014 Climb up to
    safety\n\n\U0001F4F1 5. Call for Help \u2014 Get a signal and make the rescue
    call\n\nEvery second counts. Every choice matters."
